  %div
    %h2#our-next-contract
      %a.no-underline{href: '#our-next-contract'} Our Next Contract
    %p
      In July of 2025 we began bargaining with the management at Kickstarter for our second union contract (our
      %a{href: "/contracts/2022"} first contract
      was won in 2022). From the outset we have been clear with
      management that our top priorities are codifying the
      %strong#4dww-defn 4-day, 32-hour work week (4DWW)
      as the standard and
      %strong raising the minimum salary
      for all members of the bargaining unit.
      While we are proud of the progress we have made in some areas,
      management
      %em continues to block real progress
      on the
      %span{"aria-labelledby": "4dww-dfn"} 4DWW
      and fair minimum salaries.

    %p
      For more information, see our
      %a{href: "/faq", "aria-label": "Frequently asked questions"} FAQ

