  .solidarity
    %h2#what-you-can-do
      %a.no-underline{href: '#what-you-can-do'} What You Can Do

    %p
      With management refusing to move on the 4-day week and fair pay,
      %strong we need you to stand with us more than ever.
      Here‚Äôs how you can take action today:

    .surface.solidarity__list
      .solidarity__item#solidarity-fund
        %details{name: "solidarity"}
          - go_fund_me_url = "https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-kickstarter-united-workers"
          %summary
            Donate
            %span to Our Solidarity Fund
          %div
            %p
              On Labor Day we launched our Solidarity fund on GoFundMe. If management forces a strike,
              this GoFundMe will help our most vulnerable workers weather the hardship of pay-stoppage.

            .media
              %div
                %div.gfm-embed{ data: { url: "https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-kickstarter-united-workers/widget/medium?sharesheet=undefined&attribution_id=sl:c9a70e0a-71b0-4f51-9fd6-16cb0de227df" } }
                %script{ src: "https://www.gofundme.com/static/js/embed.js", defer: true }

              %p.media__details
                If we reach an agreement without striking, we will refund any donation
                on request and roll the remaining funds into a sympathetic solidarity
                and/or hardship fund to help our fellow workers

      .solidarity__item#solidarity-petition
        %details{name: "solidarity"}
          %summary Tell Kickstarter Management: Meet Workers' Demands

          %div
            %p
              %strong We're fighting for a fair contract
              that protects our 4-day, 32-hour work
              week and raises pay for the lowest-paid employees. Unless management acts,
              we are prepared to strike on October 2. Read our
              %a{href: "https://actionnetwork.org/letters/tell-kickstarter-management-meet-your-workers-demands-to-avoid-a-strike"}
                full petition text
              and

              %strong sign now to help us avoid a strike!

            %div.embed
              %link{href: "https://actionnetwork.org/css/style-embed-v3.css", rel: "stylesheet", type: "text/css"}
              %script{src: "https://actionnetwork.org/widgets/v5/letter/tell-kickstarter-management-meet-your-workers-demands-to-avoid-a-strike?format=js&source=widget"}
              #can-letter-area-tell-kickstarter-management-meet-your-workers-demands-to-avoid-a-strike
                -# {style: "width: 70%; margin: 0 auto;"}
                -# this div is the target for our HTML insertion

      .solidarity__item#solidarity-assets
        %details{name: "solidarity"}
          %summary For Creators

          %div
            %p
              %a{href: "/creators"}
                If you're a creator and want to support us, click here to see some ways you can help!

      .solidarity__item#board-letter
        %details{name: "solidarity"}
          %summary Read our Appeal to the Board

          %div
            %p
              At the bargaining table, Kickstarter management keeps passing the buck, claiming they can‚Äôt codify the 4-day work week because
              ‚Äúthey don‚Äôt own the company.‚Äù So we went straight to the board.
            %p
              Many board members have built careers around innovative, socially driven business models and Kickstarter was chartered as a PBC to meaningfully commit to those values.
              We felt the board should know management‚Äôs actions at the table don‚Äôt align with that ethos.
            %p
              Their response? A brief dismissal of our concerns and a rejection of our invitation to the table.
            %p
              We implore the board to do the right thing and marry their actions to their words by supporting our cause.
            %p
              %strong Read the full letter below
              %embed{ src: '/docs/letter_to_the_board.pdf', type: 'application/pdf', width: '100%', height: '600px' }

      .solidarity__item#solidarity-watch
        %details{name: "solidarity"}
          - rally_recording_url = "https://us06web.zoom.us/rec/share/6OKlx_dx69PNAN5KD4RXHGUEMnJ4guwswqFwYpm00wfOAAs7JTyy847bMTYFgPfH.tu_yKEq1X0jhpnSB"
          %summary Watch Our Solidarity Rally

          %div
            %p On September 5th, we held a public virtual rally to support our fight for a fair contract.
            %p
